<section class="why-section">

<div class="why-card">

<div class="emoji">❤️👴👵</div>

<h2>1. To Care for Nigeria's Old People</h2>

<p>

We exist because every elderly person deserves to be loved and respected.
Many older people suffer from loneliness, neglect and abandonment.
Our home provides emotional support, friendship and compassionate care.
We encourage family values and treat every resident with dignity.
Our caregivers are committed to meeting both physical and emotional needs.
We create a peaceful environment where seniors feel appreciated.
Through daily interaction we reduce loneliness and depression.
We provide opportunities for recreation, worship and social activities.
Every elderly person deserves to live with joy and hope.
Our mission is to restore smiles and improve the quality of life of Nigeria's elderly people.

</p>

</div>

<div class="why-card">

<div class="emoji">🏠</div>

<h2>2. Provide Shelter</h2>

<p>

Every elderly person deserves a secure place to call home.
We provide comfortable accommodation that promotes safety and peace.
Our environment is clean, welcoming and family-oriented.
Residents enjoy privacy while remaining part of a caring community.
Our facilities are designed to support healthy ageing.
Security is available throughout the day and night.
We ensure access to clean water, electricity and sanitation.
No elderly person should experience homelessness or neglect.
Our shelter provides warmth, protection and hope.
We believe that a safe home is the foundation of a happy life.

</p>

</div>

<div class="why-card">

<div class="emoji">🏥❤️</div>

<h2>3. Provide Health Care</h2>

<p>

Healthy living is essential for every elderly person.
We promote regular medical examinations and preventive healthcare.
Residents receive proper medication and professional attention.
We encourage healthy lifestyles and physical wellbeing.
Our caregivers monitor health conditions every day.
We support mental and emotional health through counselling.
Emergency healthcare is available whenever necessary.
We work with healthcare professionals to ensure quality treatment.
Every resident deserves compassionate medical care.
Our goal is to help every elderly person enjoy a healthier life.

</p>

</div>

<div class="why-card">

<div class="emoji">🍛🥗🍎</div>

<h2>4. Provide Food</h2>

<p>

Good nutrition is important for healthy ageing.
We provide balanced meals every day.
Residents receive breakfast, lunch and dinner.
Meals are prepared under hygienic conditions.
Fresh fruits and vegetables are encouraged.
Clean drinking water is always available.
Special diets are provided when medically necessary.
Nobody should experience hunger in old age.
We believe food brings strength and happiness.
Our commitment is to nourish every elderly person with love and dignity.

</p>

</div>

